{"type":"message","id":"91951f53","parentId":"eac5470b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T05:55:48.358Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The wiki page doesn't seem to be accessible via my tools. The user seems to have already seen/read the content - they summarized it to me (\"其实咱们经营 选品主要还是跟品，或者在跟品的基础上扩展（如，增加套装，不同的组合。）\").\n\nThe user is saying that their actual product selection strategy is mainly:\n1. Following/copying products (跟品) - i.e., following what's already selling\n2. On that basis, extending/opportunistic improvements (增加套装，不同的组合)\n\nThis is a different philosophy from the detailed SOP in docs/SOP.md which has elaborate selection criteria. The user's point seems to be that the actual operation is simpler - just follow existing winners and maybe create bundles/combinations.\n\nI should acknowledge this and update my understanding. The user might be telling me that the SOP is overly complicated and the real workflow is simpler - more about following successful products and making simple extensions like bundles.\n\nLet me respond naturally based on what the user told me.\n","thinkingSignature":"72df5f1dc25e19e8f41930b6f74a0c664b834c0c5f56ec87bd26ee71b47b1e3c"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白了。你说的这个才是实际的经营逻辑：\n\n**跟品为主 + 在跟品基础上做扩展**\n\n- 跟品：别人跑通了的品，直接跟\n- 扩展：增加套装、组合变体\n\n这比 SOP 里的那些复杂评分体系要简单直接得多。我理解 SOP 是理想状态的方法论，但实际上你们更偏向\"爆款跟随 + 微创新\"——不搞那么多验证流程，跟上就行，套装组合加上去就完了。\n\n所以我应该把这个记下来，更新一下我的理解：\n- 选品核心：**跟品**，爆什么跟什么\n- 差异化手段：套装组合、变体扩展\n- 不需要复杂的三步验证那一套，跟品本身已经验证过了\n\n这个理解对吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":2858,"output":359,"cacheRead":55915,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779256531502,"responseId":"065c7fd3533147535c8d6e5f40962981"}}
