{"type":"message","id":"776275e4","parentId":"88dc4c2f","timestamp":"2026-05-20T05:58:19.403Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about the time period / timing aspect. They mentioned \"时间段呢\" - meaning what about the time period/timing, and \"文件中提到的是不是更严谨\" - suggesting that the document they shared (the Feishu wiki doc I couldn't access) mentioned something more rigorous about timing, which might overlap with or be different from what we discussed.\n\nThey seem to be pointing out that their actual practice includes timing considerations that are more rigorous than what I described. The SOP has a whole section about \"进市时间节点（应季前置）\" and seasonal/holiday timing.\n\nBut since I couldn't access the wiki doc, I should ask them to share or summarize what it says about timing, or ask if they can paste the relevant content from that document.\n\n\nI should ask them to share or paste the relevant content since I couldn't access the document.\n","thinkingSignature":"a79169d5a03afa352a9c50ed427206b0f57e68dcea05affde5c9d824268c77be"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n时间段这块我没有读到原文 —— 那个 wiki 文档一直 500 报错拿不到。\n\n你能把文件里关于时间段的部分截图或者复制过来吗？这样我才能判断：\n- 跟品的时机怎么卡（是爆了之后立刻跟，还是要等什么信号？）\n- 跟 SOP 里\"应季前置\"的逻辑是否重叠或矛盾\n\n你贴过来，我来看。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3635,"output":256,"cacheRead":56065,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59956,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779256687073,"responseId":"065c806f769a5e622803cf3104612fd4"}}
{"type":"message","id":"6298f70b","parentId":"776275e4","timestamp":"2026-05-20T05:58:58.068Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"chat_id\": \"user:ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b6fe0977e10a4c27dc9c8736e608\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Wed 2026-05-20 13:58 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_42b0f5aa88c1415647c200a3dc0a8f68\"\n}\n```\n\n上架时间\t≤30天\t超过30天的品，竞争对手已进场，无先发优势\n近7天销量增长率\t≥50%\t说明算法正在推流，产品需求处于爆发期\n总销量\t100-500单\t太少未经过市场验证，太多说明已爆，无红利空间\n评价数\t50-200条\t有真实用户反馈，可确认产品无硬伤\n同款卖家数量\t≤20个\t超过20个会启动价格战，压缩利润空间\n客单价\t3-10美元\t与当前爆款客单价一致，用户画像完全匹配，转化更顺畅\n退货率\t≤10%\t发饰类正常退货率，超过说明产品存在质量或适配问题"}],"timestamp":1779256738065}}
