{"type":"message","id":"adc9cc58","parentId":"32186696","timestamp":"2026-05-20T05:59:27.151Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now the user has shared the actual content from the file. These are product selection criteria/time-based filters:\n\n- 上架时间 ≤30天 - Products listed within 30 days, older ones have competitors with first-mover advantage\n- 近7天销量增长率 ≥50% - Shows algorithm is pushing the product, demand is in explosive growth phase\n- 总销量 100-500单 - Too few means not validated, too many means already exploded with no红利 space\n- 评价数 50-200条 - Has real user feedback, can confirm no major issues\n- 同款卖家数量 ≤20个 - More than 20 triggers price war, compresses margins\n\n\n- 客单价 3-10美元 - Matches current explosion price point, user profile matches, better conversion\n- 退货率 ≤10% - Normal for hair accessories, exceeding indicates quality or fit issues\n\nThese criteria are definitely more rigorous than what the current SOP tracks specify—they focus on timing and momentum signals that the existing tracks don't emphasize as explicitly.\n\nI need to recognize how these time-based filters actually differ from our current approach: we're looking at launch window (≤30 days), momentum indicators (≥50% 7-day growth), validated but not saturated volume (100-500 total sales), social proof through reviews (50-200), competitive landscape (≤20 sellers), pricing alignment with current winners ($3-10), and quality metrics (≤10% returns). These are essentially stage-gate criteria that tell us where a product is in its lifecycle and whether it's in the sweet spot for selection.\n","thinkingSignature":"099b9bfbbe84956bdbb5f4b6e06a7b69c4509abd41993c5c961e855bd368277b"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n这些时间维度的卡位标准比我理解的\"跟品\"要严谨得多——**本质是卡入场时间节点**，找刚启动爆发的品：\n\n| 指标 | 标准 | 含义 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **上架时间** | ≤30天 | 太晚竞争对手已进场，无先发优势 |\n| **近7天销量增长率** | ≥50% | 算法正在推流，需求爆发期 |\n| **总销量** | 100-500单 | 太少未验证，太多已爆无红利 |\n| **评价数** | 50-200条 | 有真实反馈，但还不够卷 |\n| **同款卖家数量** | ≤20个 | >20个启动价格战 |\n| **客单价** | 3-10美元 | 和爆款一致，转化顺畅 |\n| **退货率** | ≤10% | 超过说明有质量/适配问题 |\n\n---\n\n**跟 SOP 三轨的关系：**\n\n这个\"入场时间窗口\"逻辑更像是**所有轨道的统一前置过滤器**，不是单独属于某一轨。\n\n**对比：**\n- SOP 里的参数卡死是**静态参数**（月销≤500、评分≤100）\n- 这个文件是**动态信号**（30天内、增长率≥50%）\n\n两者结合才是完整逻辑：\n1. **先卡动态信号** → 找处于启动期的品（30天内+增长率爆发）\n2. **再卡静态参数** → 体量够、回评够、竞争未饱和\n3. **然后跟品或扩展** → 套装组合\n\n---\n\n**结论：**\n这组时间维度指标应该加入 MEMORY.md，作为所有选品轨道的**前置入场标准**。\n\n要不要我把这个整合更新到 SOP 和 MEMORY 里？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3487,"output":689,"cacheRead":56623,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":60799,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779256738174,"responseId":"065c80a2d736219b316eb9dc56870929"}}
