{"type":"message","id":"f9025a39","parentId":"3c33cb4d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:46:45.476Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Prepare a TikTok product link that can be opened via CDP (browser automation)\n2. They want to monitor/debug the process of getting product details\n\nThey mentioned \"tiktok商品的id 组合成可以预览的方式后在获取突破。这个操作一直没跑通，咱调试一下\" - meaning they've been trying to get product data by composing a TikTok product URL and using CDP to open it, but it hasn't been working.\n\nLet me first prepare a TikTok product link. I should use a real TikTok shop product link. The typical TikTok shop product URL format is something like:\n- https://shop.tiktok.com/product/xxx\n- Or directly on TikTok shop\n\nLet me try to get a TikTok shop product link using sorftime MCP, which we tested earlier. Let me call the tiktok_category_report or similar product function to get some product data, then we can try to open it in the browser.\n\n\nI need to be careful about the CDP approach since TikTok has anti-bot measures that could block automated access. I should prepare a product URL first and then test opening it through the browser to see what we're working with.","thinkingSignature":"e6c6832656665b94159732d47c19f8081d939ef452317b6d7bf6354f796c3871"},{"type":"text","text":"好，先通过 sorftime 拿一个 TikTok 商品链接，然后尝试用 CDP 打开调试。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_f4mcrf3igjkj_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/halei/workspace-tts && npx mcporter call sorftime-mcp tiktok_similar_product --args '{\"nodeId\": \"60490072\", \"site\": \"VN\"}' 2>&1 | head -30","timeout":20}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":249,"output":344,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":83567,"totalTokens":84160,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779259525943,"responseId":"065c8b8632435b83d78ae246c2f79302"}}
