{"type":"message","id":"c2d7fb12","parentId":"114e67e1","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:49:43.885Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The browser is on Baidu's homepage, not TikTok. The navigation to shop.tiktok.com was blocked. The browser tool has a policy that blocks navigation to certain external URLs.\n\nLet me think about this differently. The user wants to:\n1. Get a TikTok product ID\n2. Form a preview URL that can be opened in a browser for CDP\n\nThe product link format for TikTok Shop is:\n- `https://shop.tiktok.com/en/product/{product_id}` for English\n- `https://shop.tiktok.com/product/{product_id}` (with region parameter)\n\nFor Vietnam (VN), the URL would be something like:\n- `https://shop.tiktok.com/en/product/1734141996809291509?region=VN`\n\n\n- `https://shop.tiktok.com/vn/product/1734141996809291509`\n\nI'm reconsidering the approach since direct navigation seems blocked by policy. I could try using a different profile or the sandbox target instead. The real issue is that `browser` action `open` with a URL might be blocked, but `browser` action `navigate` could work differently. Let me check if the browser is already in an active session and whether I can navigate from the current Baidu page.\n\nI could try using `targetUrl` on the browser action rather than the standard URL parameter, or switch the target to \"sandbox\" instead. But actually, since the navigation was blocked by policy, maybe the user should try using their own browser instead—I'd provide the link and they could open it in their own browser and share their screen so I can watch them interact with it.\n\nLet me ask for clarification on what the user actually needs.\n","thinkingSignature":"0d3cb99c4d294373c054fc8661d69b54a3dbb9f88e2e8c1139980379648d0996"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nBrowser 打开了但导航到 TikTok Shop 被 policy 拦截了（`shop.tiktok.com` 是外部URL）。\n\n不过我已经拿到了商品数据。你想要的是：\n\n**商品链接：**\n```\nhttps://shop.tiktok.com/en/product/1734141996809291509\n```\n（Product ID: `1734141996809291509`）\n\n---\n\n**问题是：** 我的 browser 工具不能导航到 `shop.tiktok.com`，被 OpenClaw 安全策略拦截了。\n\n**两个方案：**\n\n1. **你用你自己的浏览器打开这个链接**，共享屏幕给我看，我来帮你分析页面元素和操作流程\n\n2. **配置 OpenClaw 允许 TikTok Shop 域名** — 需要改一下 browser 配置，放开 `shop.tiktok.com` 的限制\n\n你想用哪种方式？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3603,"output":514,"cacheRead":84197,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":88314,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779259764615,"responseId":"065c8c75a812b9829e2c687c12c6e3e7"}}
